Type: Package
Package: blorr
Title: Tools for Developing Binary Logistic Regression Models
Version: 0.0.9
Authors@R: person("Aravind", "Hebbali", email = "hebbali.aravind@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools designed to make it easier for users, particularly beginner/intermediate 
    R users to build logistic regression models. Includes comprehensive regression output, 
    variable selection procedure and model validation statistics.
Depends:
    R(>= 3.3.0)
